WEBVTT

00:00.943 --> 00:02.716
Previously on Damages...

00:03.100 --> 00:05.251
Hewes & associates
called me yesterday.

00:05.293 --> 00:07.345
Once Patty meets you,
there's no turning back.

00:07.399 --> 00:08.421
She'll see what I see.

00:08.438 --> 00:09.607
And she'll own you.

00:09.879 --> 00:11.781
Ms. Hewes.
What are you doing here?

00:11.830 --> 00:14.967
Kiddo, you're the first person
stupid enough to turn me down.

00:15.239 --> 00:17.439
Is there any way
I could still interview?

00:17.505 --> 00:18.536
You're hired.

00:18.592 --> 00:20.762
We are engaging in a battle

00:20.804 --> 00:22.774
with a man who will stop at nothing

00:22.808 --> 00:24.080
to preserve his fortune.

00:24.123 --> 00:26.161
<i>Arthur Frobisher told his employees</i>

00:26.332 --> 00:27.832
<i>to invest in the company</i>

00:27.995 --> 00:29.632
<i>and then sold his own stock.</i>

00:29.681 --> 00:30.920
She's on a mission here,

00:30.967 --> 00:34.035
and she won't stop till you're strung up
in the public square.

00:34.068 --> 00:36.120
Make the call.
I want some leverage.

00:36.176 --> 00:39.366
My boss wanted me
to check up on his investment.

00:39.433 --> 00:41.566
You're my sister.
How do you know Arthur Frobisher?

00:41.608 --> 00:43.962
I catered a function
for him and some businessmen.

00:44.012 --> 00:46.163
Katie, this whole case turns
on one weekend,

00:46.164 --> 00:47.196
and you were there.

00:47.197 --> 00:49.089
You want me to be
a witness against Frobisher?

00:49.371 --> 00:51.389
The new associate's been
talking to Katie connor.

00:51.410 --> 00:52.925
Whatever it takes...

00:52.989 --> 00:54.303
<i>fix this.</i>

00:54.663 --> 00:56.727
I think we have a strong case.

00:57.254 --> 00:59.985
I'd like to take it to a jury
and let them decide

01:00.025 --> 01:02.981
what Mr. Arthur Frobisher owes you.

01:03.051 --> 01:04.709
I say we end this here and now.

01:04.775 --> 01:07.118
I vote to accept the settlement.

01:07.460 --> 01:09.717
How could you have
possibly made such a

01:09.753 --> 01:11.581
catastrophic screw up?

01:11.617 --> 01:12.620
You're fired.

01:12.647 --> 01:13.670
Get out of the car!

01:13.697 --> 01:15.151
My future sister-in-law

01:15.178 --> 01:18.532
is a potential witness in
the biggest case in Patty's career.

01:18.630 --> 01:20.897
You think Patty hired
you just to get to Katie?

01:20.948 --> 01:23.360
Did she only hire me
to deliver her witness?

01:23.412 --> 01:25.209
There's no way she knew
about your friend.

01:25.393 --> 01:26.766
Saffron!

01:31.756 --> 01:32.857
Call Patty.

01:33.748 --> 01:35.027
You know what this means?

01:35.049 --> 01:36.878
If Katie can help the case, then

01:37.006 --> 01:38.208
we're doing the right thing.

01:38.245 --> 01:41.139
If Frobisher thought this would
shut her up, it's done the opposite.

01:41.436 --> 01:42.516
What's this?

01:42.535 --> 01:43.914
A souvenir for Patty.

01:44.342 --> 01:46.828
Maybe one of these days
I'll stop being impressed.

01:48.401 --> 01:49.723
Ellen figures out

01:49.919 --> 01:53.047
why you hired her, and you still
get her to deliver the witness.

01:53.255 --> 01:54.352
I like Ellen.

01:55.529 --> 01:57.706
I think she's going
to have a brilliant future.

