02:41.086 --> 02:42.252
Jesus.

02:50.429 --> 02:52.145
Ortiz! You better get in here.

03:02.049 --> 03:03.055
Hey, boss, it's Williams.

03:03.074 --> 03:04.079
We got a body.

03:09.622 --> 03:11.047
And a murder weapon.

03:15.163 --> 03:16.410
Hey, baby...

03:16.871 --> 03:19.867
All right, nobody sing
because we all know...

03:19.885 --> 03:21.637
Ellen hates singing!

03:21.669 --> 03:23.311
Whatever, whatever.

03:24.377 --> 03:25.879
But I love Fudgie the Whale.

03:25.880 --> 03:27.134
Think a wish.

03:29.956 --> 03:32.563
This next one is from
your favorite aunt and uncle.

03:32.586 --> 03:34.379
Didn't anybody read the invitation?

03:34.409 --> 03:36.243
Yeah, yeah, you
and your "no gift" bullshit.

03:36.261 --> 03:37.884
- Does anybody want anything?
- Ellen...

03:37.885 --> 03:38.906
- I'm okay.
- ...David,

03:39.280 --> 03:40.676
we know you two are real busy.

03:40.761 --> 03:42.964
A young lawyer
with a fantastic new job

03:43.020 --> 03:45.323
and a dreamy doctor fiancÃ©.

03:45.709 --> 03:46.881
Oh, the dreamiest.

03:46.924 --> 03:48.082
You both work

03:48.230 --> 03:49.240
so much,

03:49.304 --> 03:50.726
you don't even have time to eat,

03:50.904 --> 03:53.892
plus you're saving your
money to move into Manhattan.

03:53.917 --> 03:55.369
You got us an apartment?

03:55.406 --> 03:57.666
So until Katie's
restaurant opens...

03:58.548 --> 04:00.979
Aw, dinner for two
at the Olive Garden.

04:01.007 --> 04:03.182
When you're there, you're family.

04:04.034 --> 04:05.097
Thank you, Uncle Fran.

04:05.139 --> 04:06.317
Thank you.

04:07.035 --> 04:08.745
Thanks, Aunt Barb, so much.

04:08.832 --> 04:10.089
Thanks to comming.

04:17.487 --> 04:20.087
Frobisher's lawyer
calls three times a day.

04:20.113 --> 04:21.661
He's just trying to intimidate you.

04:21.747 --> 04:24.428
They just want you to sign
the confidentiality agreement.

04:24.504 --> 04:26.011
I hate these people.

04:26.065 --> 04:27.342
When you see Patty tomorrow,

04:27.366 --> 04:29.082
she'll tell you how to handle them.

04:29.339 --> 04:31.070
Every time I close my eyes,

04:31.344 --> 04:32.756
I see Saffron dead

04:32.785 --> 04:34.156
on my kitchen floor.

04:35.641 --> 04:37.442
Patty thinks
Frobisher's an asshole, too.

04:37.472 --> 04:40.355
The guy bankrupted
5,000 of his employees.

04:40.543 --> 04:43.587
I don't even care if I never step
foot in my restaurant again.

04:43.751 --> 04:46.146
Katie, we'll get through this.
Okay?

04:46.210 --> 04:47.358
The worst is over.

04:47.916 --> 04:49.868
El, your Mom wants you
to open up her present.

04:49.913 --> 04:50.972
Okay.

04:51.650 --> 04:52.968
- You guys okay?
- Wait.

04:53.216 --> 04:54.636
While I got you both here.

04:56.814 --> 04:58.599
Happy birthday, Ellen.

04:59.505 --> 05:02.123
It's a little kitsch
to add to your collection

05:02.189 --> 05:03.235
for your new apartment.

05:03.278 --> 05:05.463
Thanks, honey, you're sweet.

05:11.496 --> 05:12.600
A bookend's!

05:14.224 --> 05:15.716
- You like?
- Beautiful.

05:15.747 --> 05:16.905
It's beautiful.

